metadata.description:
A darkly humorous exploration of social issues within the abyssal deeps of Flint, Michigan. The noble octopus gazes out its window as the ghosts of the dead pass silently overhead.

Original Artwork Information

Media: Acrylic and joss paper on canvas
Dimensions: 24 x 36 x 1 5/16 inches (60.9 x 91.4 x 3.3 cm), with painted wraparound
Availability: No; original work not for sale and not included with purchase of NFT
